<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1068862>
    dc:description "FIGURES 5–7. Male terminalia of Dolichocephala spp. in Thailand, lateral view. 5. D. longicerca sp. nov.; 6. D. srisukai sp. nov.; 7. D. thailandensis sp. nov. Scale bars = 0.1 mm. Abbreviations: cl cerc—clasping cercus; distph—distiphallus; phphallus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1068862/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1068864>
    dc:description "FIGURES 17–23. Distribution of Dolichocephala spp. in Thailand at a resolution of 0.25° of latitude and longitude with symbols scaled to 0.5°. 17. D. bicolor sp. nov.; 18. D. curvata sp. nov.; 19. D. immaculata sp. nov.; 20. D. incus sp. nov.; 21. D. longicercasp. nov.; 22. D. srisukai sp.nov.; 23. D. thailandensis sp. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1068864/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1068868>
    dc:description "FIGURE 25. Phenology of adult abundance of Dolichocephala thailandensis sp. nov. caught on Doi Inthanon and Doi Phahompok and all other localities." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1068868/files/figure.png" ;
